{"title":"2020-08-21 白山","virttualPath":null,"html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-2020-08-21-白山\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2020-08-21-%E7%99%BD%E5%B1%B1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>2020-08-21 白山</h1>\n<p>横は 40km 獲得標高は 2500m ほど。</p>\n<p>チブリ尾根の登山口。この尾根は登山者が少ないので快適。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-051948-IMG_20200820_051942.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-051948-IMG_20200820_051942.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>朝露で足元はズブズブ。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-064305-IMG_20200820_064304_1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-064305-IMG_20200820_064304_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-072536-IMG_20200820_072535.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-072536-IMG_20200820_072535.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>自分で申請したチブリ尾根避難小屋は電波なし。前に確認したんだけどな… 電波と格闘するのは不毛なので先を急ぐ。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-073632-IMG_20200820_073632.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-073632-IMG_20200820_073632.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>見えてきた白山</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-084836-P_20200820_084836.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-084836-P_20200820_084836.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>すぐそこ別山</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-084840-P_20200820_084840.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-084840-P_20200820_084840.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>お参り。(心の中で)</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-090146-P_20200820_090146.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-090146-P_20200820_090146.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>気持ちいい。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-093706-P_20200820_093706.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-093706-P_20200820_093706.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>運動不足で体重重いせいか、ガレ場の下りが辛い。割と転ぶ。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-101007-P_20200820_101007.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-101007-P_20200820_101007.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-101436-P_20200820_101436.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-101436-P_20200820_101436.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-101429-P_20200820_101429.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-101429-P_20200820_101429.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"花\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>アルプス展望台。ここはポータルになるでしょ。電波もあるし後で申請しとく。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-113239-P_20200820_113239.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-113239-P_20200820_113239.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"展望台\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>平日なのに室堂はまずまずの賑い。この時期にしては… やはり少ないかな。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-121401-P_20200820_121400.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-121401-P_20200820_121400.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>大汝</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-131156-P_20200820_131156.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-131156-P_20200820_131156.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>翠ヶ池が美しい。立山のみくりが池とはまた違う。どうやら空の色が写ってさらに鮮かになるらしい。雲で青空が翳ると、少し色が落ちる。</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-134053-ricoh360.3d.thumb.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-134053-ricoh360.3d.thumb.jpg\" alt=\"myimage://2020/2020-08-20/20200820-134053-ricoh360.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>奥宮</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-141613-P_20200820_141613_1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-141613-P_20200820_141613_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>この日の締めは台湾料理の『小雪』にて</p>\n<p><a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-201731-P_20200820_201731.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-201731-P_20200820_201731.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"小雪\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-202256-P_20200820_202256_1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-202256-P_20200820_202256_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"棒々鶏\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"2020-08-20/20200820-202540-P_20200820_202540.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2020-08-20/20200820-202540-P_20200820_202540.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"牛肉炒め\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>まじでうめぇ。ホールの女の子がかわいい。</p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"随筆","updated":"2020-12-07T04:42:38","published":"2020-08-28T17:31:51"}